   - src/main/java/com/pipezfacades/client/GTFacadeQuads.java is a line-for-line port of GregTech
     CEu Modern's ICoverableRenderer.renderCovers + FacadeCoverRenderer.renderCover (LGPL-3.0).

5. Pipez (https://github.com/henkelmax/pipez) by Max Henkel is a required runtime dependency.
   No Pipez code or assets are included in this mod; it is integrated at runtime via Forge events
   and Mixins.
